com.riskgame.config

Class SpringFXMLLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.riskgame.config.SpringFXMLLoader

  • @Component
public class SpringFXMLLoader
extends java.lang.Object
    Will load the FXML hierarchy as specified in the load method and register Spring as the FXML Controller Factory. Allows Spring and Java FX to coexist once the Spring Application context has been bootstrapped.
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Piyush Thummar
